n the arbitors, and is 2hb.  I didn't, cuz I was already good at 2hs.  I do hope this helps out your decision process.  =)<br><br>Souldragoon Flamingheart<br>47th circle Paladin of Virtue<br>Fennin Ro</p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br><i>Follow virtue, and the virtuous will follow you.</i></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >1 Replies</td></tr></table><table width="100%"><tr><td class=mhback>&nbsp;</td><td class=mhback >Thread Subject</a></td><td class=mhback>Started by</a></td><td class=mhback>Replies</a></td><td class=mhback>Last Post</a></td><td class=mhback>Rating</a></td></tr><tr class=mdr>
